snippet.title: Screaming Chicken！
snippet.description: Screaming Chicken！ is a physics-based, friendship-ruining party game. Players can use weapons and traps to torture their enemies, blow them up in the air! Under the unpredictable scenes, defeat them all to be the chicken king!
